@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to FancyWorkIQ! 🚀</h1>
    
    <p class="lead">
        A modern Blazor Web App starter template for building interactive web applications with .NET 10.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-4" />

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <h2>What is WorkIQ?</h2>
            <p>
                WorkIQ (FancyWorkIQ) is a <strong>Blazor Server</strong> application that provides a solid foundation 
                for rapid web application development. Built with **.NET 10** and **Bootstrap 5**, it offers:
            </p>
            
            <ul class="list-group list-group-flush mb-4">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>⚡ Real-time Interactivity:</strong> Server-side Blazor provides instant UI updates without page refreshes
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>🎨 Modern UI:</strong> Bootstrap 5 for responsive, mobile-friendly design
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>🧩 Component-Based:</strong> Reusable components for maintainable code
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <strong>🔧 Full-Stack C#:</strong> Write both client and server code in C#
                </li>
            </ul>

            <h2>Getting Started</h2>
            <p>Explore the sample pages to see WorkIQ in action:</p>
            
            <div class="row g-3 mb-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">📊 Counter Demo</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">See Blazor's reactivity with an interactive counter example.</p>
                            <a href="/counter" class="btn btn-primary">Try Counter →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">🌤️ Weather Display</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Learn how to work with data and display it in Blazor.</p>
                            <a href="/weather" class="btn btn-primary">View Weather →</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Quick Start Guide</h2>
            <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert">
                <h5 class="alert-heading">📖 Check the README</h5>
                <p class="mb-0">
                    For detailed instructions on how to use WorkIQ in your project, including creating components, 
                    working with data, and deploying to production, see the 
                    <a href="https://github.com/prashantnayak/fancyworkiq/blob/main/README.md" class="alert-link" target="_blank">
                        comprehensive README guide
                    </a>.
                </p>
            </div>

            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <div class="row g-2 mb-3">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border bg-light rounded">
                        <strong>Components</strong><br />
                        <small>Reusable UI elements</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border bg-light rounded">
                        <strong>Routing</strong><br />
                        <small>Navigation & URLs</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border bg-light rounded">
                        <strong>Data Binding</strong><br />
                        <small>Two-way binding</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border bg-light rounded">
                        <strong>Dependency Injection</strong><br />
                        <small>Service registration</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border bg-light rounded">
                        <strong>Forms & Validation</strong><br />
                        <small>Built-in form handling</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="p-3 border bg-light rounded">
                        <strong>State Management</strong><br />
                        <small>Component state</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card bg-light">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">🎯 Quick Commands</h5>
                    <pre class="bg-dark text-light p-2 rounded"><code># Run the app
dotnet run

# Watch mode
dotnet watch run

# Build project
dotnet build

# Run tests
dotnet test</code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-light mt-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">📚 Resources</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core/blazor/" target="_blank">
                                📖 Blazor Documentation
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/" target="_blank">
                                📖 .NET Documentation
                            </a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="mb-2">
                            <a href="https://github.com/AdrienTorris/awesome-blazor" target="_blank">
                                ⭐ Awesome Blazor
                            </a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card bg-primary text-white mt-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">💡 Pro Tip</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Use <code>@@inject</code> to access services in your components and 
                        <code>@@code</code> blocks for C# logic. Keep components small and focused!
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
